---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Figma — Julien Klein">
  <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    <div style="padding: 3rem 0 1rem;">
      <a href="/ressources" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8B7355;">← Ressources</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7A5C8B; border: 1px solid #7A5C8B; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 999px;">Outil</span> <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8B7355; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 999px;">Design</span></div>
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; color: #2C2416;">Figma</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: #8B7355; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Design, maquettes et composants visuels. Utilisé pour les créas publicitaires Meta, les maquettes de landing pages clients, et les supports de présentation. Le MCP Figma permet à Claude de lire mes designs et d'en générer le code.</p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <div style="padding: 1.2rem; background: #FAF7F2; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Usage principal</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416; line-height: 1.6;">Créas Meta Ads (formats statiques + vidéo), maquettes landing pages, composants de design system client.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 1.2rem; background: #FAF7F2; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Avec Claude</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416; line-height: 1.6;">Via le MCP Figma, Claude lit directement les designs et génère le code correspondant. Design-to-code sans friction.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2C2416;">Comment je l'utilise</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;">
      {[
        "Créas Meta Ads : formats 1:1, 4:5, 9:16 en templates",
        "Maquettes landing pages pour les clients Growth",
        "Design system minimaliste pour les projets récurrents",
        "Partage de fichiers avec les équipes via lien",
        "Claude Code lit les designs via MCP pour générer le code"
      ].map((step, i) => (
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline; padding: 0.7rem 0; border-top: 1px solid #D4C9B5;">
          <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8B7355; font-family: monospace; flex-shrink: 0;">{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span>
          <span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416;">{step}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 5rem;">
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 1rem;">MCP associé</div>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
        <a href="/ressources/mcp/figma" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 6px; color: #2C2416;">Figma MCP →</a>
        <a href="/ressources/outils/meta-ads" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 6px; color: #2C2416;">Meta Ads →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
